parameters.name: CreateTimestampEnd
parameters.description: The end of the creation time range. This value is a UNIX timestamp.

parameters.name: CreateTimestampStart
parameters.description: The start of the creation time range. This value is a UNIX timestamp.

parameters.name: Name
parameters.description: The name of the custom ACL.

parameters.name: PageNumber
parameters.description: The page number. The value starts from **1**. The default value is **1**.

parameters.name: PageSize
parameters.description: The number of entries per page for a paged query. The maximum value is **100**. The default value is **10**.

parameters.name: UpdateTimestampEnd
parameters.description: The end of the update time range. This value is a UNIX timestamp.

parameters.name: UpdateTimestampStart
parameters.description: The start of the update time range. This value is a UNIX timestamp.
